    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund more initiatives to stop pollution",
        "additional_details": "So that we can have a better planet, healthier kids, fewer sick people and less disease, better mental health which could save the government money and have happier people.",
        "background": "We want the Government to provide more funding for dedicated teams to clean more beaches, sea and rivers, plant more trees, encourage more recycling and limit cars in residential areas. We also want them to invest in more clean energy.",
